{"type":"answer","id":237217,"parentType":"question","parentId":23335,"uid":9304,"contents":"马克思在故乡德国的形象：<br>\n<a href=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/EVVOEquWkAAjwcW?format=jpg&amp;name=orig\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/EVVOEquWkAAjwcW?format=jpg&amp;name=orig\" alt=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/EVVOEquWkAAjwcW?format=jpg&amp;name=orig\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<br>\n德国西南部城市特里尔由中共安置的马克思塑像，被戴上中共病毒头冠、身披中共病毒红旗。<br>\n<br>\n该塑像是马克思诞辰２００周年之际，由中共赠送的。树立5天后，遭人火烧。","date":"2020-04-12","agreeCount":4,"discussionCount":3}